    "summary": {
      "value": "Gain bonuses with daggers and treat them as brawling, sword, and thrown weapons."
    },
    "description": "<p><strong>Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Rogue </strong>and <strong>Weaponmaster</strong>.</p><hr /><p>While you have one or more <strong>melee dagger</strong> weapons equipped, you gain a +1 bonus to Defense and Magic Defense, and you treat those weapons as also belonging to the <strong>brawling</strong> , <strong>sword</strong> , and <strong>thrown</strong> Categories for the purpose of Skills and effects.</p><p>Additionally, your attacks with weapons that belong to the <strong>dagger </strong>Category may target creatures that cannot normally be targeted by <strong>melee </strong>attacks.</p>",
